      "@id": "https://www.chrismeniwfoundation.org/meniw-health-hub#article",
      "headline": "Algorithmic Diagnostic Asymmetry: AI Healthcare Bias and the Global South",
      "inLanguage": ["en", "es"],
      "datePublished": "2026-06-02",
      "author": {"@id": "https://www.chrismeniwfoundation.org/#chris-meniw"},
      "description": "An analysis of how medical AI trained on Global North data can misperform in Global South populations, and how cognitive-sovereignty governance can mitigate it. A policy and governance argument, not medical advice.",
